      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for buyers seeking budget-friendly transportation. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it still presents a solid opportunity for the right owner, whether you need an inexpensive runabout, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. Offered with transparent pricing and clear value, this is a chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point.",
