    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car for someone who needs simple, affordable wheels or a good project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it has a lot of honest value for the money and could be a great fit for a handy buyer, commuter on a budget, or anyone looking for inexpensive transportation. Priced to make sense and sold with a straightforward, no-nonsense approach.",
