      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its panels and plenty of life left for the right driver. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership, perfect for someone who appreciates a vehicle with grit, presence, and potential. Whether you need a budget-friendly daily, a handy spare, or a project to make your own, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your wallet.",
